R.  kernsmooth and mgcv do not require R 2.8.0, so they should be able 
to be upgraded, although if you can keep those back, it might be a good 
idea.  If you are using Synaptic, you can go to Package->Force Version, 
just make sure you make a note to unforce them once you upgrade to 2.8.0

